"rebirth there."

msgctxt "an8.35:4.9"
msgid ""
"Kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā brahmakāyikānaṃ devānaṃ sahabyataṃ upapajjati."
msgstr ""
"When their body breaks up, after death, they’re reborn in the company of the "
"Gods of Brahmā’s Group."

msgctxt "an8.35:4.10"
msgid "Tañca kho sīlavato vadāmi, no dussīlassa;"
msgstr ""
