"unethical."

msgctxt "an8.35:4.11"
msgid "vītarāgassa, no sarāgassa."
msgstr "And for those free of desire, not those with desire."

msgctxt "an8.35:4.12"
msgid "Ijjhati, bhikkhave, sīlavato cetopaṇidhi vītarāgattā."
msgstr ""
"The heart’s wish of an ethical person succeeds because of their freedom from "
"desire."

msgctxt "an8.35:4.13"
msgid "Imā kho, bhikkhave, aṭṭha dānūpapattiyo”ti. (8)"
msgstr "These are the eight rebirths by giving.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an8.35:4.14"
msgid "Pañcamaṃ."
msgstr ""
